  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>どうやら、謝らねばならないらしいな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>In this case, it would seem I
need to make an apology.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>31</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>生半可な気持ちなどと言って悪かった</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I was mistaken to believe you two were
going to be half-hearted about this.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>31</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>あっ、いえ。
べつに僕は……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ah, no. I'm not really...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>20</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>君はすごいね。
みんなを助けたいっていう気持ちが
すごく伝わってきたよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You're incredible.You definitely conveyed
your desire to help everyone to me.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>30</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>そんな……僕はただ
みんなの事が心配なだけで……
すごくなんてない</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>No way... I'm just worried about everyone.
I'm not that great.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>20</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>なんで褒められてんのに
ウジウジしてやがんだよっと！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Why're you bein' so wishy-washy
when you're gettin' praised like this?!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>21</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>いたっ！
痛いよぉ、スパーダ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ow! That hurt, Spada!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>20</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ヒャッヒャッヒャッヒャッ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hehehahaha!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>21</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>なに、スパーダ。
なんで嬉しそうなの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What is it, Spada?
Why are you so happy?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>20</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>へっ。
なんでもねぇよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Heh. No reason.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>21</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>……？
変なスパーダ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...?
You're weird, Spada.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>20</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
